1227
02:32:32,009 --> 02:32:34,269
[SPEAKER_24]: But nobody knows that unless you're in the room.

1228
02:32:34,489 --> 02:32:41,691
[SPEAKER_24]: So will all of these rooms have feedback systems so that the teacher doesn't have to make a phone call to say, it's 85 degrees in here.

1229
02:32:43,168 --> 02:32:46,759
[SPEAKER_24]: will know it long before it's at 85 and can do something about it.

1230
02:32:48,298 --> 02:32:52,059
[SPEAKER_17]: Yes, so not every single room will have a sensor.

1231
02:32:53,500 --> 02:32:59,342
