02:33:04,724 --> 02:33:07,705
[SPEAKER_17]: Any of the larger spaces would have its own sensors.

1235
02:33:08,285 --> 02:33:14,968
[SPEAKER_17]: And all of those talk back to a central building control system, which the facilities department has access to.

1236
02:33:16,829 --> 02:33:23,133
