1298
02:40:47,519 --> 02:40:52,722
[SPEAKER_14]: maybe like a better world out there would be really useful, I think, as we go forward.

1299
02:40:53,923 --> 02:41:10,954
[SPEAKER_26]: So I think Emily started to jump into that direction, but we can definitely provide a little bit more detail in terms of what specific systems and level of controllability that we have had in recent high school projects, specifically within the state.

