1301
02:41:16,577 --> 02:41:25,483
[SPEAKER_26]: I think at the end of the day, it really comes down to an issue of controllability of systems and the ability for an individual, in this case, the teacher to sort of control that environment.

1302
02:41:26,243 --> 02:41:26,963
[SPEAKER_26]: There are other

1303
02:41:28,923 --> 02:41:34,025
[SPEAKER_26]: sort of devices, levers that can be pulled that we can design in that we'll cover as we go forward.

1304
02:41:34,085 --> 02:41:37,426
